      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Gulgong ¶ New South Wales ¶ 23 December [1880] ¶ Baron Mueller K.C.M.G. &amp;c ¶ Dear Baron...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">80.12.23</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Charles Barnard</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M85, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS found with a specimen of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Isopogon petiolaris</seg> (MEL 1533009).</p>
               </note>Gulgong</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">New South Wales</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">23 December [1880]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition</seg>. On the specimen label, M has given the collection date as 1880.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron Mueller K.C.M.G. &amp;c</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Baron</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I herewith send you a piece of some proteaceous plant, new to me, which I should be glad to know the name of &amp; whether it is extensively known. The original plant of this portion does not stand more than a foot high when found growing. It is very rare in this neighbourhood; &amp; is found only in dry sandy soil.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I fancy I have detected fossil foliage much resembling this plant in the blackish clay of the lead whence these fossil fruits came, which I have from time to time sent you.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>For over two years past now, the "claim" has been closed where I obtained these botanical specimens, &amp; so I have not been able lately to procure any more.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Feeling sure that this member of the Proteaceae — probably a Grevillea or Hakea — was rare, I thought I could not do better than send you a specimen</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Yours faithfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Chas E. Barnard. M.D.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
